arStrings.szText: You've been trapped too long, brethren! Come to me!

The speaker for the Payloads is a Spiritborn in their 30's whose primary focus is the operation of a mage clan device based on spiritborn techniques. They'll be distracted by their efforts to operate the device while speaking.
Fly, souls! Your time in that hellhole is done!

The speaker for the Payloads is a Spiritborn in their 30's whose primary focus is the operation of a mage clan device based on spiritborn techniques. They'll be distracted by their efforts to operate the device while speaking.
There! I can sense them. Let's guide those souls to freedom!
in battle, operating a large unwieldy device (the Basin)
